        <ab>ARE DEPOSITED THE REMAINS OF</ab>
        <ab>MARY ABDY</ab>
        <ab>DAUGHTER OF JAMES BREBNER GORDON ESQ.</ab>
        <ab>OF MOORE PLACE HERTS</ab>
        <ab>AND</ab>
        <ab>RELICT OF THE LATE SIR WILLIAM ADBY BAR</ab>
        <ab>OF CHOBHAM PLACE IN THE COUNTY OF SURREY</ab>
        <ab>ENGLAND</ab>
        <ab>SHE DIED AT ROME</ab>
        <ab>MARCH IV MDCCCXXIX</ab>
        <ab>AGED LXXVIII YEARS</ab>
        <ab/>
        <ab>GENTLE PARENT. AFFECTIONATE FRIEND</ab>
        <ab>THY MEMORY LIVES IN THE HEARTS OF THE CHILDREN</ab>
      </div>
